# FlatButton

A lightweight button for secondary actions.

## Basic Usage
::TuffDemo{title="Flat Button" description="Default, primary, mini, and loading states." code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TuffFlatButton>Default</TuffFlatButton>
    <TuffFlatButton primary>Primary</TuffFlatButton>
    <TuffFlatButton mini>Mini</TuffFlatButton>
    <TuffFlatButton loading>Loading</TuffFlatButton>
  </template>
---
